Locations of Vultur gryphus.

condor.Rd

The dataset contains 510 locations of the Andean condor (Vultur gryphus) collected from 2008 to 2018. The locations are downloaded from the Global Biodiversity Inventory Facility and filtered to remove duplicates and keep only one location per raster cell of the WorldClim dataset. See references for the original databases containing the observations.

condor

Format

A data frame with 509 rows and 4 variables:

x

Longitude of the observation

y

Latitude of the observation

key

GBIF Key of the single observation

datasetKey

GBIF Key of the corresponding dataset

Source

http://www.gbif.org/
